Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人与人是靠邂逅而联系在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的朋友是朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一直连下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能整个AQUA的人都变成朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了太美了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里的美妙引擎全开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级FULL POWER的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节吹拂过城市的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上了淡淡的草帽气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天来到了新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而夏天是一年中最佳的观光季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇中的人渐渐变多 开始热闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉小镇生机勃勃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:01:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又洗了好多衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天气很好 就决定一块洗掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这是大叔的内裤 很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小姑娘 早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的腰怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能尽情享受散步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈好像有很多认识的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:28.00,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那些 充满温情的街道与人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来比我们两个本地人还要多呢 您觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸭肉炖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(346,440)}{\fs20}risotto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是送的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是香草沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太不好意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你教我把剪刀吊在屋顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能找到失物的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了它 你看 我找到我跟先生的纪念物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我才应该谢谢你的沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的店员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟灯里前辈究竟是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…平时会聊聊天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 我们还没自我介绍过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却可以那么亲密…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级不可思议的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 等会我要离开一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你走开的话 下午的练习怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我想去布拉诺岛买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆我们也取消下午的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟在灯里后面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道灯里不跟我们在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么结识朋友的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样或许能解开灯里前辈不为人知的秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vaporetto？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水上巴士的码头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 请给我两张全票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你船票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说目的地吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为Vaporetto无论坐到哪都是一个价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非蓝华前辈从来没坐过水上巴士？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代步工具只有凤尾舟 那是领航员的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～听我说完嘛 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经变得很暖和了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 外出也没这么难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 声音这么大 速度却这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人她认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到这种花 香味也很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫四照花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四照花？这个名字真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小姐你先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 还是您先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪也来坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 亚利亚社长 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就形成了一个小群体呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该都是初次见面的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到哪去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去布拉诺岛买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去超级亲密的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说啊 我们看上去会不会很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 咋了 咋咋咋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是到站了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都要撞上去才停啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上巴士真是让人昏昏欲睡的交通工具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点适应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈不可思议的秘密能解开吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又没有做什么特别的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉啊…有点犯困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 咋了 咋咋咋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说 是到站了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西还真是适应不了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲适而怀旧 又有点呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说灯里前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说水上巴士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时一个不注意 就会被「哇」地吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说水上巴士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说灯里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的皮箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮箱里面放的 说不定是尸体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨天看的侦探小说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人跟书里的尸体搬运人一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是…说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝…蓝华前辈 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她连那个人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在询问关于皮箱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来熟并不是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能随便对谁都那样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是应该过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 前辈说不定会被卷入什么事件的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…难道就不能安安静静地停船吗 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们马上帮你捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 姫社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 全都捡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妨碍各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体男也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级危机的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…噪音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 到了下一站马上转回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能到处找找看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那我们兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那10分钟后在这里集合 记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到亚利亚社长的声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是这边没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有相信自己的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT 蓝华前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得走这边对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 灯里那家伙真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不留下点记号啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像超级正确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好像在哪里看到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也这么觉得…真不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 好像活的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我以前见过那个人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是说 我也能玩这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 选哪个好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐也会让人偶跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次玩 不过我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊…小时候我看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶和旅行的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟邻居的孩子一起去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是很快乐的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 你看你看 好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 快看 真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果灯里没跟那个人熟络起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不会发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直把人家当做尸体搬运人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾随着灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能与自己遗忘的过去邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过灯里这个滤光片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能看到原本看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不起眼的东西也会开始闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 灯里就是这么一个奇妙的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级同感的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又结识了一个朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎明白为何灯里前辈有这么多朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 希望以后还会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩怎么在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级偶遇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说自己是云游四方的人偶剧师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前还来过这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 话说回来啊 你的购物计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再去吧 因为今天得到了美丽的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 今天也是充满了美丽邂逅的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐的身边总会聚集着暖洋洋的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会和蓝华姐姐与爱丽丝姐姐偶遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…那真的是偶遇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些 珍贵的光芒中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:59.15,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:12.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:27.17,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:39.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:46.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.91,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:59.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:12.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:27.17,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:39.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:46.30,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.91,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:57.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白い帽子 追いかけて笑う 響く声は高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:08.73,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}少し早い 夏の訪れに 耳を澄ましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ゆっくりと 長くなる影ふたつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな 足音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:28.01,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}金色に煌めく 夕暮れる空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:33.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波打ち際どこまでも染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:39.82,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}廻りだす季節の かけらを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:45.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そっと触れた指先に感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:50.65,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}あふれる光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:57.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}追逐着 白色帽子的笑声 响彻云际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:08.73,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}倾听着 过早到来的 夏日之声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.66,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 拉长的两个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}细碎的 脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:28.01,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}夕阳西下的天空 闪烁着耀眼的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:33.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在波浪间染遍全城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:39.82,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}细心收集不断变换的 季节的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:45.30,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}蓦然掠过指尖的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:50.65,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}消失在泛起的光芒中


